<p>This is really sucky. Weâ€™re 50/50 mac and Linux users over here and weâ€™ve found the clients to be aweful.</p>

<p>Even so, there are two issues with these (the mac and Linux version):</p>

<ol>
  <li>Canâ€™t drag and drop the files.</li>
  <li>Canâ€™t access the interface if splash is running</li>
</ol>

<p>The first we canâ€™t solve. The second you can resolve by creating another network (sometimes) and or logging in via the splash.</p>

